700102f-a.title: Bronx: 144th Street (East) - Morris Avenue
700102f-a.text:
E. 14ith Sreet, north side, east from Morris Avenue. The Street makes a sharp bend to the right, running in a southeasterly direction for a short distance.
P. L. Sberr  April 29, 1941

701473f-a.title: Bronx: Morris Avenue - 143rd Street (East)
701473f-a.text:
Morris Avenue, east side, south from East 143rd street. Note the
old house on the left.
shows the east side of the Avenue, looking north from 142hd  Street.
P. L. Sperr  April 29, 1941
